name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 89: Spooky House

content.html:
Dear Internet,On this weeks episode, we talk about how spooky is too spooky for a neighborhood, bachelorette party nicknames, and a haunted shirt.We would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet.Sincerely,The coHosts- Nick, Jennifer, Michael, and Tim Lanning!Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!
